title: Gorgeous Split-level townhome in beautiful CherryHurst neighborhood
posting_body: ['Split-level townhome located in the Cherryhurst area with its neighborhood feel and its proximity to bountiful bars and restaurants; and much more.', 'Home has an open modern design, three bedrooms, two baths, two car attached garage, North/South exposure, wood burning fireplace, induction cooktop, Wolf and Bosch appliances, quartz countertops, patio area, two balconies and the many windows provide for an abundance of natural light.', 'Call Or Text', 'show contact info', '*****Tenant requirements are no broken leases, gross monthly income is 3x the rent, 615+ credit, no evictions, no broken leases, no criminal history', '** Pet Description:', 'Pet deposit will depend on size, weight, type and number of pets', 'Call Jess to setup your showing today!', "Head over to my IG: Outragejessre for more available properties or let's talk about your criteria and I'll put together your custom list of applicable properties!"]
